    • entity.Exam
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class Exam
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The department and all its fields were included in the diagrams. The department is used to store data for an exam a student has done or a private information created by a teacher. We've added additional fields to the columns that will include exam details in various tables that display exam details.
